name: position type
description: How the position has been retrieve: GPS or estimate (if GPS is not available ex: in a tunnel).

name: position signalQuality
description: Quality of the position signal when acquire through GPS.

name: Alert active
description: Describe if the alert is active or inactive.

name: Alert startPosition coordinates
description: Coordinates where the alert occurs. Comes with signalQuality heading & type.
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values: longitude latitude and altitude.

name: Alert endPosition coordinates
description: Coordinates where the alert stoped. Comes with signalQuality heading & type.
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values: longitude latitude and altitude.

name: Alert label
description: The label that describes what happened to raise this alert.

name: Energy supply
description: Describe vehicle energy supply. This object could exists in both instance in case the vehicle is Hybrid.

name: Preconditioning program enable
description: Display whether this program is enabled or not.

name: Charging
description: Return if the electric vehicle is charging or not.

name: State of ambiant luminosity
description: Boolean state of ambiant luminosity (day or night)

name: Door lock sate
description: Describe lock state for each doors of the vehicle.

name: Preconditioning state
description: The state of the preconditioning feature.

name: Preconditioning Error state
description: Cause of failure in case preconditioning has not been started.

name: Preconditioning Reccurence program
description: Recurrence of the program. None: means no recurrence. Daily: repeated over the week.

name: Doors lock state
description: Describe lock state for all the doors of the vehicle.

name: eCall state
description: State of the eCall emergency system.

name: Fuel instant consumption
description: Instant consumption for vehicles for thermic vehicle.

name: Preconditionning program slot
description: Program slot number as you can select one between various preconditioning programs.

name: Charging rate
description: Charging speed expressed in autonomy per hour.

name: Preconditioning program start time
description: The program start time formatted using the duration format based on ISO 8601.

name: Charging remaining time
description: Remaning time before the battery is fully charged.

name: Charging Next delayed time
description: Time at which charging is scheduled.

name: Preconditioning program occurence days
description: Days of the week affected by recurence.

name: Park assist front
description: State of the front park assist

name: Park assist rear
description: Sate of the rear park assist

name: ACCR State
description: State of the Adaptive Cruise Control Regulation

name: AEBS State
description: State of Advanced Emergency Braking System

name: AFIL State
description: State of Lane Departure Warning System

name: ARTIV State
description: Respect of inter vehicle time assist (ARTIV)

name: Lighting Light
description: Information about vehicle lights (other than turn signals).

name: Days Before Maintenance
description: Number of days before next maintenance.

name: Mileage Before Maintenance
description: Number of kilometers before next maintenance.

name: Trip current Info
description: Retrieve information about the current navigation.
unit_or_value: latitude, longitude, nextStreetName, town, city, province, country

name: engine class
description: Class electric or class thermic vehicle.

name: thermic engine energy
description: Fuel type of a thermic vehicle.

name: Fuel Unit
description: Retrieve what fuel unit is currently in use in the HMI.

name: HMI time hour
description: HMI current hour of the day.
unit_or_value: latitude, longitude, nextStreetName, town, city, province, country

name: HMI time minute
description: HMI current minute of the hour.

name: HMI UTC offset
description: HMI current off set with UTC.

name: HMI distance Unit
description: Current distance unit used within the HMI

name: HMI theme
description: Current theme within the HMI. See webportal colour theme.

name: HMI internet status
description: Retrieve current internet status of the vehicle

name: HMI album name
description: Current album playing within the HMI

name: HMI artist name
description: Current artist playing within the HMI

name: HMI track number
description: Current track number playing within the HMI

name: HMI Total tracks
description: Get total number of tracks on the connected media

name: HMI track name
description: Current track playing within the HMI

name: position
description: Coordinates of the vehicle as specified in RFC3339.
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values: longitude latitude and altitude.

name: Trip End Position
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values, longitude latitude and altitude.

name: Trip current ETA
description: Retrive current ETA for an ongoing navigation.

name: Privacy state
description: Privacy state of the vehicle requested by the driver

name: HMI radio frequency
description: Gets the currently selected radio frequency of the car in kHz.

name: HMI radio preset
description: Indicates the saved preset corresponding to the current frequency.

name: HMI Radio PTY
description: Returns the program type as defined by either RDS or RBDS. Possible values are [0-31].

name: HMI Radio RDS
description: Return true if the current radio stations supports RDS, false otherwise.

name: HMI Radio TA
description: Returns true if traffic announcement is available.

name: HMI Country
description: Gets the country currently selected by the user.

name: Fleet Name
description: Name of the fleet to which this vehicle belongs.

name: Fleet Description
description: Description of the fleet to which this vehicle belongs.

name: Fleet identifier
description: Unique identifier of the fleet to which this vehicle belongs.

name: collision tipped
description: Information about the tipped of the vehicle when the collision occured

name: collision side
description: area of the vehicle affected by the collision

name: Trip completion
description: Determines whether this trip have is finished.

name: Trip faults
description: The faults of a finished or in progress trip. This means that we lacked data from the vehicle to complete the trip description during one of its step (starting, progressing, or finishing).

name: Trip Start position
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values, longitude latitude and altitude.

name: Trips alerts
description: Alerts related to a trip. See alerts for more info.
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values, longitude latitude and altitude.

name: Telemetry of a trip
description: Telemetries for a trip. Available: privacy, engine type, energy type, brakes, transmissions, adas, lightening, ignition, door state, battery, beltWarning, eCall trigering, luminosity, air temperature, odometer, acceleration, speed, pace, moving, location, maitenance.
unit_or_value: See telemetries categorie for more info.

name: remote doors
description: Lock or unlock the vehicle`s dorr remotly.

name: remote immobilization
description: Toggle immobilization on/off throught remote command.

name: monitor doors state
description: Receive notification on door state change.

name: monitor position
description: Receive notification when a certain position is triggered

name: monitor telemetries
description: Receive notification when your telemetrie model is triggered.

name: monitor alerts
unit_or_value: 2 to 3 values, longitude latitude and altitude.

name: HMI Speed Unit
description: Current speed unit used within the HMI

name: Driving behavior mode
description: Driving mode selected by the driver.

name: Wiping blade speed
description: Wiping speed. Available only if wiping blade state is active.
